Synonym: alpha1D; alpha 1D; A1D; Alpha 1D- adrenoreceptor; Alpha 1D-adrenoceptor; Alpha adrenergic receptor 1a; Alpha-1A adrenergic receptor; Alpha-1D adrenergic receptor
Alpha1D receptor.Definition: Alpha adrenergic receptor that is found in the rat aorta, and is genetically different from the other alpha1 receptors.
